# Non-mobile workspaces — excluded from EAS build uploads.
# Mobile only depends on @repo/types (+ @repo/tsconfig transitively).
# Keeping these out prevents pnpm from installing their deps on the EAS
# worker (e.g. sharp in apps/api, which fails to build from source).
apps/api/
apps/web/
apps/web-v2/
apps/ios-mockups/
packages/eslint-config/
packages/ui/

# Build artifacts and logs
**/.next/
**/.turbo/
**/coverage/
apps/*.log
*.log

# Large root-level docs and reports
PRE_LAUNCH_AUDIT_*.md
PRE_LAUNCH_FIX_PLAN_*.md
STRIPE_TEST_MODE_RUNBOOK.md
STRIPE_TESTING_CHECKLIST.md
SEO-COMPARISON-REPORT.md
appstore-listing.txt
content/

# Sibling lockfiles that accumulated
pnpm-lock\ *.yaml
